{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-diaries-markdown-remark-frontmatter-slug-jsx","path":"/diaries/go-to-taxkorgan/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>习惯性的早上七点半起床，然后就感受到了第一个小小的新疆震撼，天，是黑的，两个小时时差果然名不虚传。</p>\n<p>简单吃了点零食，等到司机师傅出发后就是接人、坐车、感受喀什人的一天从抓饭开始。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1eb887f62903bf1d965a499b3aef8ca0/e1596/2023-10-02-grap-rice.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.84662576687117%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"grab rice\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1eb887f62903bf1d965a499b3aef8ca0/6aca1/2023-10-02-grap-rice.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1eb887f62903bf1d965a499b3aef8ca0/d2f63/2023-10-02-grap-rice.jpg 163w,\n/static/1eb887f62903bf1d965a499b3aef8ca0/c989d/2023-10-02-grap-rice.jpg 325w,\n/static/1eb887f62903bf1d965a499b3aef8ca0/6aca1/2023-10-02-grap-rice.jpg 650w,\n/static/1eb887f62903bf1d965a499b3aef8ca0/7c09c/2023-10-02-grap-rice.jpg 975w,\n/static/1eb887f62903bf1d965a499b3aef8ca0/01ab0/2023-10-02-grap-rice.jpg 1300w,\n/static/1eb887f62903bf1d965a499b3aef8ca0/e1596/2023-10-02-grap-rice.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>从路上和司机大哥有一搭没一搭的聊天中得知，喀什主要是一些农业，矿业，因为和阿富汗，巴基斯坦接壤，所以会有一些进出口贸易，也因为内地人在这里做生意，把喀什的物价拉的也比较高，城里一碗拉面就要 20 元，价格直逼一线城市。同时作为边境城市，下面的塔县可以看到很多走私一些或者倒腾一些假货香烟的巴铁。</p>\n<p>路上也发生了一段不是那么愉快的小插曲，旅行社没有提前定我的酒店。虽然最终的结果还算不错，这里暂且按下不表。</p>\n<p>途径白沙山-白沙湖，白沙山真的很神奇，旁边的山都是石头山，只有她披了一层厚厚的白沙，山下紧贴着瓦蓝的白沙湖（维语发音 QiongKuaileBashi），湖对面就是公格尔峰所属的雪山山脉。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/27d2314469cca615974bfafbb735d7f9/e1596/2023-10-02-qiongkuailebashi.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.84662576687117%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Qiongkuaile bashi\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/27d2314469cca615974bfafbb735d7f9/6aca1/2023-10-02-qiongkuailebashi.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/27d2314469cca615974bfafbb735d7f9/d2f63/2023-10-02-qiongkuailebashi.jpg 163w,\n/static/27d2314469cca615974bfafbb735d7f9/c989d/2023-10-02-qiongkuailebashi.jpg 325w,\n/static/27d2314469cca615974bfafbb735d7f9/6aca1/2023-10-02-qiongkuailebashi.jpg 650w,\n/static/27d2314469cca615974bfafbb735d7f9/7c09c/2023-10-02-qiongkuailebashi.jpg 975w,\n/static/27d2314469cca615974bfafbb735d7f9/01ab0/2023-10-02-qiongkuailebashi.jpg 1300w,\n/static/27d2314469cca615974bfafbb735d7f9/e1596/2023-10-02-qiongkuailebashi.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>走过白沙湖，就是慕士塔格冰川公园，所属海拔 4000 米，上冰川要坐区间车，候车大厅里面吸氧罐的卡卡声不绝于耳。候车厅到冰川脚下（海拔 4500 米）之间，一片戈壁，明明是一个俊俏的小中巴车，12 公里的路程活生生开出了越野拉力赛的感觉，中巴车开成了叙利亚战损版。</p>\n<p>到达冰川之后能有明显的高原反应，明明吸了一大口气，但就是有种吸不够的感觉。要到达冰川还要在网上爬公里，海拔上升 100 米。爬到一半就有一种平时冲刺跑了四公里的感觉，股四头和臀大肌开始堆积乳酸。当然如果不想受这份罪，可以请“人”替自己——上下山可以花200块钱体验骑马上下山。花钱上下山是不可能的，一方面是因为自己确实状态还不错，另一方面看着那一匹匹马上下山往返跑骨瘦嶙峋的样子，竟然有点心有戚戚然，甚至有一丝牛马般的共鸣……</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/493906777224efb35b42dac9db36103a/ac99c/2023-10-02-muztagh-horse.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.12883435582822%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"muztagh horse\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/493906777224efb35b42dac9db36103a/6aca1/2023-10-02-muztagh-horse.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/493906777224efb35b42dac9db36103a/d2f63/2023-10-02-muztagh-horse.jpg 163w,\n/static/493906777224efb35b42dac9db36103a/c989d/2023-10-02-muztagh-horse.jpg 325w,\n/static/493906777224efb35b42dac9db36103a/6aca1/2023-10-02-muztagh-horse.jpg 650w,\n/static/493906777224efb35b42dac9db36103a/7c09c/2023-10-02-muztagh-horse.jpg 975w,\n/static/493906777224efb35b42dac9db36103a/01ab0/2023-10-02-muztagh-horse.jpg 1300w,\n/static/493906777224efb35b42dac9db36103a/ac99c/2023-10-02-muztagh-horse.jpg 1536w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>虽然最后一公里花了我快半个小时的时间，但是一切的努力都是值得的，在落日前一刻，爬上冰川前的山包，搭上一个小石堆，让它代我在雪山上看日出日落。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3bbfaf3c448671cea1df8283601a01bf/e1596/2023-10-02-muztagh-stone.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.84662576687117%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"muztagh stone\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/3bbfaf3c448671cea1df8283601a01bf/6aca1/2023-10-02-muztagh-stone.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3bbfaf3c448671cea1df8283601a01bf/d2f63/2023-10-02-muztagh-stone.jpg 163w,\n/static/3bbfaf3c448671cea1df8283601a01bf/c989d/2023-10-02-muztagh-stone.jpg 325w,\n/static/3bbfaf3c448671cea1df8283601a01bf/6aca1/2023-10-02-muztagh-stone.jpg 650w,\n/static/3bbfaf3c448671cea1df8283601a01bf/7c09c/2023-10-02-muztagh-stone.jpg 975w,\n/static/3bbfaf3c448671cea1df8283601a01bf/01ab0/2023-10-02-muztagh-stone.jpg 1300w,\n/static/3bbfaf3c448671cea1df8283601a01bf/e1596/2023-10-02-muztagh-stone.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/acb5384be7908892fe374485802334a6/e1596/2023-10-02-muztagh-glacier.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.84662576687117%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"muztagh glacier\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/acb5384be7908892fe374485802334a6/6aca1/2023-10-02-muztagh-glacier.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/acb5384be7908892fe374485802334a6/d2f63/2023-10-02-muztagh-glacier.jpg 163w,\n/static/acb5384be7908892fe374485802334a6/c989d/2023-10-02-muztagh-glacier.jpg 325w,\n/static/acb5384be7908892fe374485802334a6/6aca1/2023-10-02-muztagh-glacier.jpg 650w,\n/static/acb5384be7908892fe374485802334a6/7c09c/2023-10-02-muztagh-glacier.jpg 975w,\n/static/acb5384be7908892fe374485802334a6/01ab0/2023-10-02-muztagh-glacier.jpg 1300w,\n/static/acb5384be7908892fe374485802334a6/e1596/2023-10-02-muztagh-glacier.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>到达塔什库尔干的时候已经是十点了，然后就开始住宿囧途了，先去塔县迎宾馆，结果告诉我们，能查到我的名字，但是不知道房号，折腾了半个小时终于知道房号了，结果被告知拼的人不愿意，被放了鸽子，只能再临时找酒店。找到酒店之后，虽然新酒店实在说不上干净，但是拼住的房客是一个维族大哥，人很客气友好，还很健谈。作为一个老喀什人，给我推荐了很多喀什特色老店。这些老店后来在我的喀什最后一天都一一种草，算是计划外的惊喜了。</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"October 02, 2023","slug":"/go-to-taxkorgan","title":"前往塔什库尔干"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"f1e814c8-bdb0-5b96-a1d0-95418cded9cf","frontmatter__slug":"/go-to-taxkorgan","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"go-to-taxkorgan"}}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}